 * - stage_category_eval: Per-category score breakdown
 *
 * All inserts wrapped in transaction - rolls back on any error.
 *
 * @param messageId - Gmail message ID
 * @param result - Classification result from pipeline
 * @throws Error if messageId is invalid or database operation fails
